title: DJ Bosch
abstract: DJ Bosch aka Tobias is resident DJ at Multisex party happening at Ohm/Berlin. The Multisex party promotes clarity on the dance floor along with diverse music. Depending on the booking, they create different dancing moods with classy tunes that craft a pure and effective house, disco and techno sound. Multisex is an attempt to encourage non-verbal communication on the dance floor. The goal is to get people together while dancing free. Besides that Tobias is doing the lights here at the CCC Lounge and is a regular light operator at Berghain/Panoramabar in Berlin.
